<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About Us - Avecena</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.1.2/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50">

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav class="bg-blue-900 text-white p-6 shadow-lg">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
      <div class="text-3xl font-extrabold">
        <h1>Avecena</h1>
        <p class="text-xl">Home Tuitions</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="flex space-x-8 text-lg font-medium">
        <li><a href="#overview" class="hover:text-blue-300">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#vision" class="hover:text-blue-300">Vision</a></li>
        <li><a href="#mission" class="hover:text-blue-300">Mission</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- About Us Hero Section -->
  <header class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 via-indigo-500 to-purple-600 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-wide">About Avecena Home Tuitions</h1>
      <p class="text-xl font-medium max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        At Avecena, we are redefining education with a focus on creativity, critical thinking, and hands-on learning.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Overview Section -->
  <section id="overview" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 text-center mb-12">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        Avecena Home Tuitions was founded with the belief that education should be dynamic, interactive, and meaningful.
        Our unique approach bridges the gap between traditional learning and modern educational needs. By emphasizing
        creativity, problem-solving, and collaboration, we aim to nurture confident, well-rounded individuals ready to
        face the challenges of the future.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:space-x-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Philosophy</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We believe that every student is unique, and learning should adapt to individual strengths and passions.
            Our programs are designed to empower students to think creatively and critically while fostering a love
            for lifelong learning.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex-1 mt-8 md:mt-0">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Our Impact</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            With a proven track record of success, we have helped countless students achieve academic excellence
            while developing skills that extend beyond the classroom. Our impact is measured not just in grades but
            in the growth of confident, capable learners.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision Section -->
  <section id="vision" class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 text-center mb-12">Our Vision</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center leading-relaxed">
        Our vision is to revolutionize the education system by prioritizing hands-on learning and creativity. We strive to
        create an environment where students are inspired to innovate and express themselves while acquiring essential
        knowledge and skills.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400" alt="Our Vision" class="rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section id="mission" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-800 text-center mb-12">Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Empowering Students</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our mission is to provide students with the tools they need to excel in their academic pursuits while
            preparing them for real-world challenges. By fostering a growth mindset and encouraging curiosity, we
            help students unlock their full potential.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4">Promoting Creativity</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            At Avecena, we celebrate creativity as a cornerstone of success. Our programs encourage students to
            explore their passions, think outside the box, and develop innovative solutions to problems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-blue-900 text-white py-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-lg">&copy; 2024 Avecena Home Tuitions. All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>

</html>